7. When tarball is available:
* Update blueprint @ [5]
* Build Windows, AppImage, macOS x86+arm64 packages on CD (release/2.12 branch)
* Test packages and upload them
	kdecp labplot-2.12.0-arm64.dmg labplot-2.12.0-x86_64.AppImage labplot-2.12.0-x86_64.dmg labplot-2.12.0-x86_64-setup.exe ftp://upload.kde.org/incoming
* Fill another sysadmin ticket at https://go.kde.org/u/systickets including the checksums to upload the packages

