* Update package in MS Partner Center (appxupload) for Windows App Store https://partner.microsoft.com/en-us/dashboard
* Update Flatpak @ https://github.com/flathub/org.kde.labplot/blob/master/org.kde.labplot.json
* Upload tarball and packages to https://sourceforge.net/projects/labplot/ and update default downloads
* Ping Scarlett Moore to update Snap and chtof to update Chocolatey package


